        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if PUF ID is cleared successfully</para></listitem><listitem><para>XPUF_ERROR_PUF_ID_ZERO_TIMEOUT if timeout while clearing PUF ID </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
